.TH GENERATE_FILES 1 "March 2026" "AutoReadme" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
generate_files \- Generate Apache auxiliary files from README.md table
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B generate_files
[\fB\-\-no-htaccess\fR] [\fB\-\-create_header\fR] [\fB\-\-ignore\fR \fIFILE\fR...] [\fB\-\-ignore-patterns\fR \fIPATTERN\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B generate_files
parses the file table in README.md and generates Apache web server auxiliary files:
.IP \(bu 2
.B .htaccess
Apache server directives with file descriptions
.IP \(bu 2
.B .contents
Alternative AccessFileName with file descriptions
.IP \(bu 2
.B .info
File information for the tree command
.PP
The tool also processes special markdown comments in README.md that contain Apache directives.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-no-htaccess
Do not generate .htaccess file
.TP
.B \-\-create_header
Write full header into .header.html (requires Apache IndexOptions +SuppressHTMLPreamble)
.TP
.B \-\-ignore \fIFILE\fR...
List of sensitive files/directories to deny access to. Default: .backups .git ..netrc .netrc .ssh Downloads notfolder.jpg
.TP
.B \-\-ignore-patterns \fIPATTERN\fR...
Patterns of file names to deny access to. Default: *.a *.o *.so *.bak
.br
When generating
.BR .htaccess ,
entries from
.B ~/.config/autoreadme/ignore_htaccess.txt
are appended if that file exists.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B README.md
Source file containing the file table and optional Apache directives
.TP
.B .htaccess
Generated Apache configuration file
.TP
.B ~/.config/autoreadme/ignore_htaccess.txt
Optional user-specific deny patterns appended to generated
.BR .htaccess .
.TP
.B .contents
Generated alternative Apache configuration
.TP
.B .info
Generated file information for tree command
.SH APACHE DIRECTIVES
Special markdown comments in README.md can contain Apache directives:
.PP
.nf
[.htaccess AddIcon "/.icons/oscar.jpg" tmp   ]: #
[.contents AddDescription "Custom desc" file.txt]: #
.fi
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Generate all files with defaults:
.B generate_files
.TP
Generate without .htaccess:
.B generate_files \-\-no-htaccess
.TP
Ignore additional files:
.B generate_files \-\-ignore secret.txt private/
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR generate_html (1),
.BR autoreadme (1),
.BR generate_table (1)
.SH AUTHOR
AutoReadme project
